  17 Dec 2007; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org>
  +scipy-0.6.0-r3.ebuild:
  Revert clapack patch (see bug #197527) and take care of LDFLAGS as numpy

*scipy-0.6.0-r2 (18 Oct 2007)

